import { List, ListItem, ListItemText, ListItemButton } from '@mui/material'
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'

const BottomHeader = () => {
  return (
    <List component='nav'
      sx={{
        display: "flex", flexDirection: "row", alignContent: "center",
        padding: "4px 20px", width: '70%', justifyContent: 'center'
      }}>

      <ListItem>
        <Link to="/">
          <ListItemButton sx={{  textDecoration:'none', padding: '8px' }}>
            
            <ListItemText primary="novedades" primaryTypographyProps={{fontSize: '0.9rem', fontWeight: '500' }}
              sx={{ textTransform: 'uppercase' }} />
         
          </ListItemButton>
        </Link>
      </ListItem>
      <ListItem>
      <Link to="/viaje">
        <ListItemButton sx={{ padding: '8px' }}>
          <ListItemText primary="viaje" primaryTypographyProps={{ fontSize: '0.9rem', fontWeight: '500' }}
            sx={{ textTransform: 'uppercase' }} />
        </ListItemButton>
        </Link>
      </ListItem>
      <ListItem>
        <ListItemButton sx={{ padding: '8px' }}>
          <ListItemText primary="bolsos" primaryTypographyProps={{ fontSize: '0.9rem', fontWeight: '500' }}
            sx={{ textTransform: 'uppercase' }} />
        </ListItemButton>
      </ListItem>
      <ListItem>
        <ListItemButton sx={{ padding: '8px' }}>
          <ListItemText primary="carteras" primaryTypographyProps={{ fontSize: '0.9rem', fontWeight: '500' }}
            sx={{ textTransform: 'uppercase' }} />
        </ListItemButton>
      </ListItem>
      <ListItem>
        <ListItemButton sx={{ padding: '8px' }}>
          <ListItemText primary="accesorios" primaryTypographyProps={{ fontSize: '0.9rem', fontWeight: '500' }}
            sx={{ textTransform: 'uppercase' }} />
        </ListItemButton>
      </ListItem>
      <ListItem>
        <ListItemButton sx={{ padding: '8px' }}>
          <ListItemText primary="hombre" primaryTypographyProps={{ fontSize: '0.9rem', fontWeight: '500' }}
            sx={{ textTransform: 'uppercase' }} />
        </ListItemButton>
      </ListItem>
      <ListItem>
        <ListItemButton sx={{ padding: '8px' }}>
          <ListItemText primary="rebajas" primaryTypographyProps={{ fontSize: '0.9rem', fontWeight: '500' }}
            sx={{ textTransform: 'uppercase' }} />
        </ListItemButton>
      </ListItem>
    </List>
  )
}

export default BottomHeader
